    <!-- Info Screens -->
    <string name="help_content">Here you can find detailed information on how to use the Yupay Turismo application to boost your rural business.\n\n1. Visit registration: Go to the Visits or Home tab and press the + button. You can register the country of origin, the estimated expense (as a range, fixed value, or exact amount), and the services you provided.\n\n2. Management Charts: On the Home screen, use the Day, Week, Month, and Year selectors to see the evolution of your visits and understand which times are best for your business.\n\n3. Interactive Map: Visualize which countries your tourists come from. This helps you know which audience to target or which languages to prepare for better.\n\n4. Synchronization: You can link multiple devices (phone and tablet) using the QR code in your profile so that all records stay updated without the need for internet at the time.\n\n5. Entrepreneur Tips: Listen every day to a personalized recommendation in your language to improve the hospitality and quality of your services.</string>
    <string name="privacy_content">At Yupay Turismo, your privacy and that of your business data are our top priority.\n\n1. Local Storage: All the information you register (visits, names, profiles) is stored securely and privately directly in your device\'s memory. It is not uploaded to any public "cloud" without your control.\n\n2. Direct Synchronization: When you link two devices, the data transfer occurs directly between them through your local network (WiFi or Hotspot), ensuring that your records do not leave your work environment.\n\n3. Data Use: Visit data is used exclusively to generate your statistical reports and personal management charts. Yupay Turismo does not share, sell, or use your information for advertising or third-party commercial purposes.\n\n4. Permissions: We request access to the camera solely to scan linking QR codes, and network permissions for synchronization between your own devices.</string>

